title: Did the White House Give Lesley Stahl a Blank Book of Trump’s Healthcare Accomplishments?
subtitle: "A perfect metaphor for the Trump presidency," critics claimed. What really happened?
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In October 2020, White House Press Secretary Kayleigh McEnany gave "60 Minutes" reporter Lesley Stahl a large book of U.S. President Donald Trump's healthcare accomplishments, which was blank.
